        "creation_date": 1446617321,
        "body": "<p>You need to use a static import of the method:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>import static lightsOut.LightsOutModel.checkWin;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Once you import, you can directly use them, <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>checkWin();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/guide/language/static-import.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Here is the official reference<\/a><\/p>\n",
